Garb, I don't know what put the bug up your keester regarding my post, but leaving aside the bombast about vultures, etc., your point seems to be that if someone manages to spawn a mob, its not cool for anyone else to kill it, regardless of whether the person(s) spawning it had the capability of killing it.  I disagree.  <br>
